snippet.title: Ink Inside - Coming to All Platforms Trailer
snippet.description:
Ready for an extraordinary journey with the spirit of a classic Saturday morning cartoon?

We are thrilled to announce that we will be publishing #InkInside, the most charming action RPG from Blackfield Entertainment, on ALL platforms this year (including last gen consoles!) 

What are you waiting for? Add #InkInside to your Steam wishlist now!

https://bit.ly/InkInsideOnSteam
